{"page":1,"prev_page_endpoint":null,"next_page_endpoint":null,"total_pages":1,"reasons":[{"created_at":"2013-07-17T05:16:40Z","content":"Because everyone needs a little additional time to pay their bills sometimes, especially those on a fixed income.","like_count":3,"author_name":"Phyllis Elam","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56730691"},{"created_at":"2013-07-21T06:15:34Z","content":"Sometimes things happen to people that make meeting the monthly bills , it just happens...","like_count":2,"author_name":"Deb Blake","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47820103"},{"created_at":"2013-07-20T14:22:59Z","content":"if it wasn't for my mother, I would be homeless! she is in her 70's! so I know what it is like to need help paying your bills!","like_count":2,"author_name":"joan mobley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57079121"},{"created_at":"2013-08-02T02:21:41Z","content":"single parent no support","like_count":2,"author_name":"delores yates","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/58407894"},{"created_at":"2013-07-20T10:59:40Z","content":"been in their shoes","like_count":2,"author_name":"Kim Ferguson","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57066081"},{"created_at":"2013-07-17T06:08:32Z","content":"People need help and a little patience.  Life is not all about moneyHelp your fellow human as long as they are trying.  ","like_count":2,"author_name":"Doris Tucker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/47336853"},{"created_at":"2013-07-25T05:34:46Z","content":"considered moving there until I was told $600. 00 deposit. By the time you make all the deposits expected...just said FORGET IT.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Mary Sykes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57493874"},{"created_at":"2013-08-02T03:27:21Z","content":"It is hard to pay the large amts in summer all at once...on SSI. It would help if those months you could defer a portion over to catch up. Have to go low on meds or food when it is $100 more than normal because of high temps! I have medical issues and can not be in heat. ","like_count":2,"author_name":"Deborah Dunning","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/58411116"},{"created_at":"2013-07-20T00:44:39Z","content":"been in the same situation before","like_count":2,"author_name":"terri ford","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57041999"},{"created_at":"2013-07-25T11:29:50Z","content":"I have family and friends here and I know for some it would be quite helpful!!!!\r\n\r\n","like_count":2,"author_name":"kim dugger","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57518639"},{"created_at":"2013-07-19T02:38:41Z","content":"Because I would like to see this plan put in to action all across Kentucky for all of us in this situation of a limited budget..Thank You ,Ms. Janetta Boarman","like_count":2,"author_name":"Janetta Boarman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56942549"},{"created_at":"2013-07-17T07:20:42Z","content":"I have seen family members be cold in the winter over a few days time between due dates and paychecks.. Single mothers with children choosing between MMU and kids bed and food. I don't understand why arrangements can't be made as long as something is paid every month.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Chrissie Bryant","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5963713"},{"created_at":"2013-07-26T02:32:48Z","content":"It is very hard for low/medium income customers to come up with the large sums that Madisonville Utilities ask of us. I think not transferring deposits is appalling, unless the customer has a history of not paying their bill on time, but loyal customers should be permitted to transfer. In winter/summer months when electric is used at a greater need, there should be a set payment plan for those that  find it hard to make ends meet during these hard months, a lot have children/geriatrics in the home and it is a must to have utilities available to them. Madisonville has gotten outrageous on the Utilities in the last couple of years.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Sherry Woolfolk","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57599664"},{"created_at":"2013-07-20T17:51:47Z","content":"We live on a very tight budget and struggle to get ours paid most time in the summer cause its always an average of 400.00 or more why i dont know mmu is so much higher than ku and I don't know how that is","like_count":2,"author_name":"Cesar Sifuentes","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57092523"},{"created_at":"2013-07-17T04:39:52Z","content":"well Madisonville could care less, its all about the money, but I will sign","like_count":2,"author_name":"Janice Thomas","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/5408883"},{"created_at":"2013-07-18T23:03:50Z","content":"We all get into a tight spot now and again. ","like_count":2,"author_name":"Georgia Gilbert","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56915155"},{"created_at":"2013-08-04T21:36:01Z","content":"People on fixed incomes need some help from time to time.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Melena Lamb","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/58633961"},{"created_at":"2013-07-20T08:15:50Z","content":"I to am on disability and struggle just to pay the bill because of medical reasons. To be quite blunt I don't understand why the Water Dept. still puts flouride in the water when even the FDA says it is one of the most toxic chemicals known to man. That in itself would cut back cost a lot. Thank you for your understanding.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Jeffery Davis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/23956667"},{"created_at":"2013-07-20T14:07:49Z","content":"Because I have had to struggle at times and know how it feels to not have enough to go around sometimes, but THANK GOD he has blessed me with the ability to take care of things now but we never know when it will change.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Patricia Medelle","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57078237"},{"created_at":"2013-07-24T02:51:03Z","content":"I had paid $250.00 in 2011 with payments on time. When I moved I was unable to 'transfer\" my utilities. They wanted almost $600.00 more for a deposit which I was unable to do. My utilities were still on at my old place and I was unable to transfer them...They had to be put in someone else's' name. I am a volunteer firefighter and I work full time and my city (the best town on earth) does not have my back. Because of the way my paychecks fall, it is hard to pay in full sometimes. This is \"unfair\" and \"unethical\". ","like_count":2,"author_name":"Kamea Golay","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57363501"},{"created_at":"2013-07-25T17:36:36Z","content":"Madisonville is my hometown and its hard on everyone.especially if your credit is not that great .Now days people need help.Stop keeping when they are down.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Vanessa Huff","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57543365"},{"created_at":"2013-07-25T20:47:04Z","content":"Because so many are on fixed incomes or a low praying job. Instead of just letting those WHO have paid on time consistantly, being able to be on a Budget. Let the low income family be on a Budget. That way they know What their Bill is every month. ","like_count":2,"author_name":"christina williams","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57553712"},{"created_at":"2013-07-17T04:48:52Z","content":"I too live in Madisonville and it is extremely hard sometimes for me to pay the entire balance and  I also draw SSI. They recommended me NOT to get on budget due to the bill would, for whatever reason, be higher. ","like_count":2,"author_name":"Theresa McMican","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56727748"},{"created_at":"2013-07-25T03:13:53Z","content":"To help those that need it.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Edith  Taylor ","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/28717954"},{"created_at":"2013-07-24T04:18:06Z","content":"I have been in the position before of not being able to pay on time, bad things do happen to good people.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Anita Allen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/13502047"},{"created_at":"2013-07-26T21:02:48Z","content":"the utility company needs to realize that there are people who cannot afford to pay these prices. People are going hungry because their bills are so ridiculously high. these companies act like they are the only ones asking for money and they are forgetting the fact that there are all kinds of people demanding payments. ","like_count":2,"author_name":"Jerry Cummins","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57710082"},{"created_at":"2013-08-04T21:45:32Z","content":"it's hard to make $1000 a month pay house payments, phone bills, utilities, and buy food for 4 people. We need help.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Jessica Lamb","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/58634474"},{"created_at":"2013-07-25T13:21:21Z","content":"I have had this problem in the past and I sympathize with anyone in this situation. ","like_count":2,"author_name":"Carol Adcock","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57527204"},{"created_at":"2013-07-18T22:31:44Z","content":"I lived in Madisonville my whole life. I broke my neck working in a factory in Madisonville and lost everything. MMU wouldn't work with me at all on my bills. I wasn't trying to get out of the bills just needed more time to pay them. Not everyone has the money like they think we do. All we're asking is work with us and don't push us out of \"The best town on earth\" but live up to that name.","like_count":2,"author_name":"Marlon Lamb","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/56912157"},{"created_at":"2013-07-27T23:32:23Z","content":"This hits close to home for me as my dad and other family live in Madisonville. I also know too the struggle of not being able to pay bills on time. ","like_count":2,"author_name":"Bethany Moore","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57825701"},{"created_at":"2013-07-27T01:06:20Z","content":"Water is a needed thing to exist. It should be FREE the sewage charge is OUTRAGEOUS!!!!!!","like_count":2,"author_name":"David Tolliver","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57731922"},{"created_at":"2013-07-20T00:55:01Z","content":"I am on disability and sometimes it is hard to pay my complete bill in full.... I have lived in my present house for over 12 years, never had my utilities disconnected, always paid by \"agreed\" date when they used to allow it. The new rules that requires me to \"pay in full\" or be disconnected Is ridiculous!!! My good credit that I have established with the Madisonville Municipal Utility company over the past 20 plus years is not being taken into consideration. Poor people need an \"intervention\" in this matter please...","like_count":1,"author_name":"Phyllis Elam","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/57042366"},{"created_at":"2013-07-21T01:34:59Z","content":"I signed and Stared this petition because i am tired of seeing ppl struggle to get by and we all know that  M.M.U. is taking advantage of us  because they can ,'' IT NEEDS TO BE STOPPED ASAP''several friends and relatives  , friends and others  have moved to the next town over because it was it was cheaper This town is no longer the best town on earth in my opinion , not to mention how often i struggle myself and not able to get out and work , barely getting through the day  in so much pain ,just doing my daily chores but keep smiling to up lift someone's day and  not to let others see  my pain .God Bless!\r\nPS. \r\nAll of you that have signed thank you for the support , please share and like, then help by encouraging others to do the same ty .","like_count":1,"author_name":"Beverly Bean","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/27271555"}]}